Sentencas: In this study, we will report our investigation for La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.5O3-delta (LSCrM) based anodes impregnated with solutions of cobalt (Co) nitrate.
Titulo: Cobalt-impregnated La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.5O3-δ anodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A YSZ supported SOFC with pure LSCrM anode and La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 (LSM) cathode exhibits the maximum power density (P-max) of 58.7 and 5.2 mW cm(-2) at 850 degrees C in dry H-2 and dry CH4.
Titulo: Cobalt-impregnated La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.5O3-δ anodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: After the modification of anode with Co nitrate, the P-max reaches 196.2 mW cm(-2) in dry H-2 and 28.5 mW cm(-2) in dry CH4, about 3.34 times and 5.48 times increase, respectively.
Titulo: Cobalt-impregnated La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.5O3-δ anodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results indicate that Co is also a potential catalyst for LSCrM anode.
Titulo: Cobalt-impregnated La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.5O3-δ anodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Moreover, the effect of impregnation amount of catalyst on the cell performance is also evaluated in this study.
Titulo: Cobalt-impregnated La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.5O3-δ anodes for solid oxide fuel cells
